        <item>
            <title>中国深圳首设电动车专用道，减少电动自行车与汽车冲突</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/shenzhen-baoan-bike-lanes/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=shenzhen-baoan-bike-lanes</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/shenzhen-baoan-bike-lanes/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:48:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
